00:19:38.720 --> 00:19:40.931
- That's really nice.
- Mmm, mmm, mmm...

319
00:19:51.108 --> 00:19:52.818
"Beautiful dripping fragments.

320
00:19:52.985 --> 00:19:54.528
The negligent list

321
00:19:54.695 --> 00:19:56.780
of one after another,

322
00:19:56.947 --> 00:19:59.199
as I happen to call
them to me.

323
00:19:59.366 --> 00:20:01.076
Or drink to them.

324
00:20:01.243 --> 00:20:03.203
The real poems,
what we call poems,

325
00:20:03.370 --> 00:20:06.582
being merely pictures.
The poems of the privacy of the night.

326
00:20:06.748 --> 00:20:09.585
And of men like me.

327
00:20:09.751 --> 00:20:11.879
This poem,
drooping shy and unseen,

328
00:20:12.045 --> 00:20:15.090
that I always carry.
