I didn't see you there.

425
00:25:24.691 --> 00:25:25.651
You kinda scared me.

426
00:25:29.029 --> 00:25:30.989
Becoming friendly
with that boy down there.

427
00:25:33.700 --> 00:25:34.827
Yes.

428
00:25:36.119 --> 00:25:37.579
Bring him
to the house on Sunday.

429
00:25:37.746 --> 00:25:39.581
I want to meet
this young man.

430
00:25:39.748 --> 00:25:42.376
Okay.

431
00:25:42.543 --> 00:25:43.585
Good night, Daddy.

