00:26:06.066 --> 00:26:07.484
Bishop Stevens
told me that.

438
00:26:07.651 --> 00:26:11.113
Olivier, please remove the... the liquor
decanter from in front of my husband.

439
00:26:11.280 --> 00:26:12.573
I think he's had
a little too much to drink.

440
00:26:12.739 --> 00:26:15.242
- I don't get it.
- Pay attention.

441
00:26:15.409 --> 00:26:17.870
So, what do
you do, Noah?

442
00:26:18.036 --> 00:26:20.747
