444
00:26:25.085 --> 00:26:26.461
Oh, that's lovely, dear.

445
00:26:26.628 --> 00:26:28.213
Thank you.

446
00:26:28.380 --> 00:26:30.757
If you don't mind my asking, uh,
how much do you make at your job?

447
00:26:30.924 --> 00:26:32.593
Uh, how much money
do I make?

448
00:26:32.759 --> 00:26:34.553
Mm-hmm.

449
00:26:34.720 --> 00:26:37.264
About 40 cents an hour.

450
00:26:39.933 --> 00:26:42.769
Yeah, it's not much,
