451
00:26:42.936 --> 00:26:45.063
And I...
I save most of it.

452
00:26:46.857 --> 00:26:48.275
Let's eat. Shall we?

453
00:26:48.442 --> 00:26:51.570
Yes! Oh,
it looks delicious.

454
00:26:54.031 --> 00:26:57.284
So Noah, you and Allie have been
spending a lot of time together.

455
00:26:58.952 --> 00:27:01.371
You must be very fond
of each other.

456
00:27:03.207 --> 00:27:05.417
It's getting
pretty serious, huh?

457
00:27:05.584 --> 00:27:07.169
Yes, ma'am.

458
00:27:07.336 --> 00:27:11.465
Well, summer's almost gone.
