459
00:27:11.632 --> 00:27:14.259
You know, Charleston's
only a couple of hours away.

460
00:27:16.428 --> 00:27:18.388
But Allie's going
to Sarah Lawrence.

461
00:27:20.307 --> 00:27:21.767
Didn't she tell you?

462
00:27:21.934 --> 00:27:24.061
